  "instructions": [
    "Pit and chop 1 cup ripe dates.",
    "In a small bowl, mix 2 tbsp almond butter, 1 tbsp coconut aminos, 1 tsp olive oil, and 1 tbsp chopped mint leaves.",
    "Combine dates with the dressing, stirring until sticky and smooth.",
    "Add 1/4 cup toasted cashews and 1/4 cup thinly sliced red onion, mixing gently.",
    "Chill for 10 minutes for optimal texture and flavor.",
    "Serve immediately with a drizzle of extra-virgin olive oil."
